    "content": "In the early hours of the morning, a mother sat at her computer, scrolling through endless websites and apps. Her eyes glazed over as she scrolled down the list of options, each one more distracting than the last. She was tired, but not from sleep; instead, it was the exhaustion of trying to keep up with the ever-changing world around her. The screens were like mirrors, reflecting back the chaos and confusion that surrounded her."
