    "title": "The Angry Mom and Her Computers",
    "content": "It was a typical day in the life of a Victorian mother, as she sat at her computer, scrolling through social media feeds and checking emails. She had just finished cooking dinner for her family when she heard a loud crash from the kitchen. Without thinking, she rushed to investigate, only to find that her laptop had been smashed into a million pieces. The screen was shattered, the keyboard was bent, and the mouse was nowhere to be found. Her heart sank as she realized that she would have to start all over again from scratch."
